Privacy Policy
We prioritize the security and confidentiality of the personal information you provide. Please review this policy to understand our privacy practices.
By accessing the Ferryscanner Platform—meaning our website, (
www.ferryscanner.com
), or the
Ferryscanner
®
application
available on iOS and Android devices (collectively referred to as “our Platform”)—you agree to the practices described here.
